        <dependency-check.version>12.1.0</dependency-check.version>
        <jacoco-maven-plugin.version>0.8.12</jacoco-maven-plugin.version>
        <!--
            OSS Index credentials — supplied at invocation time via
            -DossIndex.user=... -DossIndex.token=... or CI secrets.
            Empty defaults mean unauthenticated local runs degrade
            gracefully (analyzer disables itself) instead of failing.
            See docs/maven/OSSINDEX-TOKEN-IMPLEMENTATION.md.
